Name: Soulfarm

text: Soulfarm (formerly known as Inasense) is an American Jewish rock band based in New York City. They were founded in 1991 by C Lanzbom and Noah Solomon.[1]  Their music is a mix of mainstream rock, Jewish/Middle Eastern, bluegrass, and Celtic influences (among others).[2] Soulfarm is a fixture on the New York City club circuit. The band has also traveled extensively throughout the world.
